%S A393743 1,1,4,21,183,1918,22908,290492,3844168,52442130,733062632,10453488195
%N A393743 Number of free polyominoes in the {8,7} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%F A393743 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q; also P{p,q}(q+1) = P{p,oo}(q+1) + floor((p-1)/2) - floor((3+q(p-2))/2). In this case, p=8, q=7 and P{p,oo} = A389937.
%Y A393743 Cf. A393739, A393740, A393741, A393742, A393744, A389937.
%K A393743 nonn,more,new
%O A393743 1,3
